A '''core bomb''' was a type of [[Bomb/Legends|explosive]]. [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] searched for traces of a core bomb by identifying its key components, [[Accellerite/Legends|accellerite]], and [[magnopium ferrocongregate]] by way of [[vapor sampler]]s. [[Malta]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]], in a discussion with fellow Hutts [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] and [[Embra]], commented that he would have handled the [[Besadii/Legends|Besadii]] [[Spice/Legends|spice]] raid by arming a "[[Death/Legends|suicidal]] zealot" with a core bomb and dropping the individual into the clan's [[Ylesia/Legends|Ylesian]] base of operations from the hull of a [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]].

